      <title>艾伯塔省因成本和收益问题解雇养老金管理委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/alberta-fires-pension-manager-s-entire-board-over-costs-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔投资管理公司 (Alberta Investment Management Corp.) 的整个董事会被省政府解雇，省政府表示，该基金经理已经增加了薪酬和员工数量，但并未产生可接受的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/alberta-fires-pension-manager-s-entire-board-over-costs-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称选举不会对美联储产生短期影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-says-election-to-have-no-near-term-effect-on-fed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，美国总统大选不会对美联储货币政策产生短期影响。美联储决策机构联邦公开市场委员会一致决定将联邦基金利率下调至 4.5% 至 4.75% 区间后，鲍威尔在新闻发布会上发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-says-election-to-have-no-near-term-effect-on-fed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
